"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932360-Simon-Biles-Olympics-2024-gymnastics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Simone Biles underlined her professionalism and sportmanship at the2024 Olympicsafter missing out on a gold medal in her final event in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.601268051942092e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles was hoping to win her fourth gold medal of the 2024 Olympics after emerging victorious in the team event with USA, before coming back to seal the individual all-around gold and dominated the vault final on Sunday.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 365, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999720890480416, \"rank\": 2.2911693516540468e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the American could only claiming silver in the floor event in Paris, with Brazil's Rebeca Andrade deservedly scooping the top prize for an outstanding routine on the mat.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999998660014261, \"rank\": 1.243188655063733e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.601268051942092e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9529911667054707, \"rank\": 0.0379615311932962, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 454, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebeca Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebeca_Andrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, who had cut a frosty look earlier afterblaming the tense atmosphere in the crowd for forcing her into a mistakein the beam event, was much happier at the end of the floor competition despite losing to Andrade.\", \"from\": 543, \"to\": 759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999937622306, \"rank\": 6.112404205122281e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair were joined by USA's Jordan Chiles, who controversionally snatched the bronze medal away from Romania's Ana Barbosu following a review of her score by the judges.\", \"from\": 761, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999720890480416, \"rank\": 2.2911693516540468e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}, {\"begin\": 864, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9999893127217477, \"rank\": 1.0390609346951746e-05, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of simply celebrating their medals with the national anthem, USA duo Biles and Chiles elected to give Andrade the ovation she deserved.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999720890480416, \"rank\": 2.2911693516540468e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1044, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999937622306, \"rank\": 6.112404205122281e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone says Jordan asked Simone, \\\"Should we bow to her?\\\"\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1091, \"end\": 1097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"score\": 0.5369120091955687, \"rank\": 0.8378428604395262, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Grand_Prix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Simone replied, \\\"Absolutely.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\\"It was just the right thing to do.\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"https://t.co/VLXxDWGS1i  Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999440661, \"rank\": 5.601268051942092e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1418, \"end\": 1430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9994932675756605, \"rank\": 0.000506989117103642, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to USA Today, Chiles approached her compatriot and apparently asked her USA colleague Biles: \\\"Should we bow to her?\\\"\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"score\": 0.9999999998804014, \"rank\": 1.1942020303076585e-10, \"text\": \"USA Today\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Today\"}, {\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1590, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999720890480416, \"rank\": 2.2911693516540468e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"referring to Andrade.\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1645, \"end\": 1652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999937622306, \"rank\": 6.112404205122281e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Showing her classy character, Biles replied: \\\"Absolutely\\\" and the pair kneeled before gesturing to the Brazilian gymnast, 25.\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When she was quizzed later on about on their admirable act, Biles simply said \\\"it was just the right thing to do\\\".\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, 27, had been under pressure following an earlier mistake during the balance beam routine, where she fell off the bar - as several other competitors did - and finished outside the medal positions in fifth.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But she regained her composure and delivered a fine routine on the floor.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2186, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With Andrade setting the benchmark at 14.166 early on, Biles knew she had to deliver a big performance.\", \"from\": 2187, \"to\": 2290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999937622306, \"rank\": 6.112404205122281e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She nailed the opening tumble with a double back and landed it smiling.\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Then she pulled off a full twist into a double back, although she landed outside the mat markings which resulted in her being marked down.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her score of 14.133 fell just short of Andrade, putting her in the silver medal position.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2550, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999937622306, \"rank\": 6.112404205122281e-09, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With two more gymnasts to go, 17-year-old Sabrina Maneca-Voinea could only score 13.700 and, despite a requested inquiry, the result stood.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Spellman\", \"score\": 0.9330549420975244, \"rank\": 0.0717482485563168, \"text\": \"Sabrina\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Spellman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabrina_Spellman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2735, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  USA's Jordan Chiles was the last to go, but she could only place fifth with her score of 13.666.\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2985, \"end\": 2998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jordan Chiles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Chiles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, an appeal to the judges was granted and her score was upgraded to 13.733, lifting her into the bronze medal position and allowing Biles to take silver.\", \"from\": 3076, \"to\": 3236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 3238, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 3283, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 3353, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3508, \"end\": 3521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3160966830145445e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3557, \"end\": 3570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3160966830145445e-23, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q